# AMR-GigaWord 200k

# ::id 0 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok martin brodeur moved within two wins of tying patrick roy 's nhl career record when he made ## saves in the new jersey devils ' #-# victory over the calgary flames on tuesday .
# ::alignments
(m / move-01
      :ARG1 (p / person
            :name (n / name
                  :op1 "martin"
                  :op2 "Brodeur"))
      :ARG2 (w / within
            :op1 (w2 / win-01
                  :quant 2)
            :op2 (t / tie-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :ARG1 (r / record
                        :mod (c / career)
                        :poss (p2 / person
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "Patrick"
                                    :op2 "Roy")))))
      :time (m2 / make-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (s / save-03
                  :ARG0 p
                  :location (w3 / win-01
                        :ARG0 (t2 / team
                              :name (n3 / name
                                    :op1 "Devils"))
                        :ARG1 (f / flame
                              :mod (c2 / calgary))
                        :mod (j / jersey
                              :ARG1-of (n4 / new-01))
                        :time (d / date-entity
                              :weekday (t3 / tuesday))))))

# ::id 1 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok with three business days remaining this year , there is still time for some tidying up of your financial affairs .
# ::alignments
(t / time
      :mod (s / still)
      :purpose (t2 / tidy-up-02
            :ARG1 (a / affair-02
                  :ARG1 (y / you)
                  :ARG2 (f / finance))
            :mod (s2 / some))
      :ARG1-of (c / cause-01
            :ARG0 (r / remain-01
                  :ARG1 (d / day
                        :quant 3
                        :mod (b / business))
                  :time (y2 / year
                        :mod (t3 / this)))))

# ::id 2 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the british and irish prime ministers gathered northern ireland 's rival factions around the same negotiating table wednesday and told them they must strike a power-sharing deal by a nov. ## deadline .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (g / gather-03
            :ARG0 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (p / person
                        :ARG0-of (h / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c / country
                                    :name (n / name
                                          :op1 "Great"
                                          :op2 "Britain"))
                              :ARG2 (m / minister
                                    :mod (p2 / prime))))
                  :op2 (p3 / person
                        :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                              :ARG1 (c2 / country
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Ireland"))
                              :ARG2 (m2 / minister
                                    :mod (p4 / prime)))))
            :ARG1 (f / faction
                  :ARG0-of (r / rival-01
                        :ARG1 c2)
                  :location (a3 / around
                        :op1 (t / table
                              :ARG2-of (n3 / negotiate-01)
                              :ARG1-of (s / same-01))))
            :time (w / wednesday))
      :op2 (t2 / tell-01
            :ARG0 a2
            :ARG1 (o / obligate-01
                  :ARG1 a2
                  :ARG2 (s2 / strike-01
                        :ARG0 a2
                        :ARG1 (d / deal-01
                              :ARG2 (s3 / share-01
                                    :ARG1 (p5 / power)))
                        :time (d2 / deadline
                              :mod (n4 / nov.))))
            :ARG2 f))

            :name (n / name

                  :op2 "Soong")

                  :ARG1 (p2 / political-party
                        :name (n2 / name
                              :op1 "First"
                              :op2 "Party"))
                  :ARG2 (c / chairman)))
      :ARG1 (j / join-01
            :polarity -
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a / ally-01
                  :ARG2 (s2 / stabilize-01
                        :ARG1 (n3 / nation))
                  :ARG1-of (f / form-01
                        :ARG0 (p3 / person
                              :name (n4 / name
                                    :op1 "Chen"
                                    :op2 "Shui-bian")
                              :ARG0-of (h2 / have-org-role-91
                                    :ARG2 (p4 / president)))
                        :ARG1-of (p5 / propose-01
                              :ARG0 p3
                              :time (a2 / after
                                    :op1 (e / elect-01
                                          :time (w / weekend
                                                :mod (t / this))))))))
      :time (w2 / wednesday))

                        :op1 "France")))

                  :op2 "D dementieva")

                  :name (n5 / name
                        :op1 "Open"

                        :op3 "Sue"))

      :purpose (t / title
            :ord (o2 / ordinal-entity
                  :value 1
                  :range (t2 / temporal-quantity
                        :quant 2
                        :unit (y / year)))
            :poss p))

# ::id 1881 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok since the middle and lower reaches of the yangtze river , the nenjiang river and the songhuajiang river were hit by huge flood disasters , many foreign leaders have sent messages to the chinese leaders , expressing sympathy and concern for the victimized people .
# ::alignments
(a / and
      :op1 (m / message-01
            :ARG0 (p / person
                  :ARG0-of (l / lead-02)
                  :mod (f / foreign)
                  :quant (m2 / many))
            :ARG2 (p2 / person
                  :ARG0-of (l2 / lead-02
                        :ARG1 (c / country
                              :name (n / name
                                    :op1 "China")))))
      :op2 (e / express-01
            :ARG0 p
            :ARG1 (a2 / and
                  :op1 (s / sympathize-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 (p3 / person
                              :ARG1-of (v / victimize-01)))
                  :op2 (c2 / concern-01
                        :ARG0 p
                        :ARG1 p3)))
      :time (s2 / since
            :op1 (h / hit-01
                  :ARG0 (d / disaster
                        :mod (f2 / flood-01)
                        :mod (h2 / huge))
                  :ARG1 (a3 / and
                        :op1 (r / reach
                              :mod (r2 / river
                                    :name (n2 / name
                                          :op1 "Yangtze"))
                              :mod (m3 / middle))
                        :op2 (r3 / reach
                              :ARG1-of (h3 / have-degree-91
                                    :ARG2 (l3 / low-04
                                          :ARG1 r3)
                                    :ARG3 (m4 / more)))
                        :op3 (r4 / reach
                              :mod (r5 / river
                                    :name (n3 / name
                                          :op1 "Nenjiang"
                                          :op2 "River"))
                              :mod (r6 / river
                                    :name (n4 / name
                                          :op1 "Songhuajiang")))))))

# ::id 1882 ::amr-annotator ISI-AMR-01 ::preferred
# ::tok the joy for chinese paralympian li dongmei was short-lived as her gold had been deprived after the review of classification .
# ::alignments
(c / cause-01
      :ARG0 (d / deprive-01
            :ARG1 (g / gold
                  :poss (p / person
                        :name (n / name
                              :op1 "Li"
                              :op2 "Dongmei")
                        :mod (p2 / paralympian)
                        :mod (c2 / country
                              :name (n2 / name
                                    :op1 "China"))))
            :ARG2 p
            :time (a / after
                  :op1 (r / review-01
                        :ARG1 (c3 / classify-01))))
      :ARG1 (l / live-01
            :ARG1 (j / joy
                  :poss p)
            :ARG1-of (s / short-07)))
